\"/bonus-accuracy-disclaimer/\">Bonus Accuracy Disclaimer</a> \u2022\n    Responsible play: <a href=\"/responsible-gambling/\">Responsible Gambling</a>\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<!-- BLACKLIST TABLE (SINGLE SOURCE OF TRUTH) -->\n<div class=\"tcs-review-block\" style=\"max-width:960px;margin:0 auto 24px;\">\n\n  <style>\n    /* =========================\n       Scoped polish: BLACKLIST TABLE ONLY\n       Fixes:\n       - No overlap in last column\n       - Larger logos\n       - Buttons contained (no hover shift clipping)\n       - Table stays within 960px (wraps; no horizontal scroll)\n       - Mobile-safe stacking for last column\n       ========================= */\n\n    .tcs-blacklist-help { margin: 0 0 14px; color:#c7d2ff; line-height:1.7; }\n    .tcs-blacklist-help strong { color:#ffdd55; }\n\n    .tcs-blacklist-legend{\n      display:grid;\n      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));\n      gap: 12px;\n      margin: 12px 0 18px;\n    }\n    .tcs-blacklist-legend .tcs-blacklist-chip{\n      border: 1px solid rgba(255,204,51,0.18);\n      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.18);\n      border-radius: 14px;\n      padding: 12px;\n      text-align: left;\n    }\n    .tcs-blacklist-legend .tcs-blacklist-chip b{\n      display:block;\n      color:#ffcc33;\n      font-size:.82rem;\n      letter-spacing:.10em;\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      margin-bottom: 6px;\n      font-family: 'Oswald', Arial, sans-serif;\n    }\n    .tcs-blacklist-legend .tcs-blacklist-chip p{\n      margin: 0;\n      color:#a8c7ff;\n      font-size:.92rem;\n      line-height:1.55;\n    }\n\n    /* Table: fit, wrap, no horizontal scroll */\n    .tcs-blacklist-table{\n      width:100% !important;\n      table-layout: fixed !important;\n      border-collapse: collapse;\n      background-color:#050518;\n      color:#e3e9ff;\n      border-radius: 14px;\n      overflow:hidden;\n    }\n    .tcs-blacklist-table th,\n    .tcs-blacklist-table td{\n      border-bottom: 1px solid #1a1a3d;\n      padding